      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;table-of-contents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Table of Contents&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#table-of-contents&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#table-of-contents&#34; &gt;Table of Contents&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#overview&#34; &gt;Overview&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#features&#34; &gt;Features&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#monetization-strategies&#34; &gt;Monetization Strategies&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#freemium-model&#34; &gt;Freemium Model&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#api-access&#34; &gt;API Access&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#browser-extension-monetization&#34; &gt;Browser Extension Monetization&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#ad-based-revenue&#34; &gt;Ad-Based Revenue&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#white-labeling-and-licensing&#34; &gt;White-Labeling and Licensing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#data-analytics-and-reports&#34; &gt;Data Analytics and Reports&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#architecture&#34; &gt;Architecture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#core-classes&#34; &gt;Core Classes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#conclusion&#34; &gt;Conclusion&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Overview&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The IPConverter program is a comprehensive software application designed to provide users with a variety of powerful tools and features related to IP addresses. Built primarily in C++, it will leverage external libraries and APIs where necessary to expand its capabilities. This application will serve as a go-to tool for developers, network administrators, marketers, and cybersecurity professionals.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
